Fossil is a simple, high-reliability, distributed software configuration
management system with these advanced features:
  - Integrated Bug Tracking, Wiki, and Technotes
  - Built-in Web Interface
  - Self-Contained - Fossil is a single self-contained stand-alone executable.
  - Simple Networking - No custom protocols or TCP ports (HTTP, HTTPS or SSH).
  - CGI/SCGI enabled
  - Autosyn
  - Robust & Reliable
  - Free and Open-Source
